
do macro substitution when a line is read in to be tokenized for assembly.

	\${symbol} ==> decimal number, symbol's value

	.shift
	.push stackname,value,value...
	.pop stackname,symbolName,symbolName...
	.popall stackname
	.goto labelname   [pops all intervening levels]

":name" in first column is ripped-off, and used as a target for .goto
